"with different security and compliance requirements, and facilitate the "
"boundary protection. You put each subsystem into a separate service mesh,"
" preferably on a separate network. You connect the Istio meshes using "
"gateways. The gateways monitor and control cross-mesh traffic at the "
"boundary of each mesh."
